<TEXT>
the supreme court is even better than night 
court on tv and it would be neat to be a member say some of the 
hundreds of school kids who wrote to the court to help celebrate 
its 200th anniversary 
the court received multicolored and handprinted cards from 
elementary school students around the country as it marked its 
