roses are red violets are blue supreme court is great and a 
happy birthday to you wrote brandi bryant a fourthgrader from 
grafton va 
classmate billy francavilla told the justices youre better 
than night court a television show 
and grafton fourthgrader kristi downs who probably doesnt 
