uprising that has been raging in the occupied lands since december 
1987 they are ready for it he said they want to fulfill 
the commandment of living in the land of israel eretz israel 
the rabbi said the hebrew phrase eretz israel is a reference 
to the biblical land of israel that also includes the west bank 
