that struck the whittier area on oct 1 1987 that one measured 
59 and together with a 53magnitude aftershock on oct 4 killed 
eight people injured more than 200 and caused 358 million in 
damage 
the richter scale is a measure of ground motion as recorded on 
seismographs an earthquake of 5 can cause considerable damage and 
6 severe damage 
