who violate federal gun laws calling for mandatory prison sentences 
will be launched in eight cities later this month officials said 
friday 
the project achilles task forces will be in place by march 26 in 
new york philadelphia los angeles chicago miami detroit 
washington and phoenix said bureau of alcohol tobacco and 
firearms spokeswoman dot koester 
the atf conducted a similar fourmonth armed career criminal 
operation in washington last year as a prelude to the upcoming 
project and made quite an impact she said 
in addition to making numerous arrests because they kept 
hitting certain areas again and again the neighborhood people 
started coming out and cheering the agents on koester said 
out of that developed a hotline which the neighbors then used 
