nzo said the anc leaders meeting with mandela for the first 
time since president fw de klerk lifted a 30year ban on the anc 
on feb 2 also decided to open headquarters offices in 
johannesburg south africa immediately 
while the anc was outlawed in south africa its political and 
guerrilla leaders have operated their headquarters from zambia 
asked to elaborate on his new role in the anc mandela was 
noncommital 
