children 
her youngest child 8monthold sean is adopted his natural 
mother an unmarried teenager lived with the vernon family during 
pregnancy 
hes just the sort of baby who might have been terminated as 
they like to call it mrs vernon said then laughed and added 
but i feel a bit guilty using him as a sales point 
